========
TrashCan
========

:Author: Yen-Ju Chen <yjchenx at gmail>
:License: BSD license
:NOTE: Highly unstable. Use it on your own risk.

TrashCan is a trash can implementation of freedesktop trash specification.
See trash.html or http://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Standards_2ftrash_2dspec
It only implements home trash under user's home directory.
It depends on XWindowServerKit.

User Defaults
-------------
Key: TrashCanPosition
Value: 0 (Left Bottom), 1 (Right Bottom)

